didate for menopause, but no mechanistic or clinical-stage detail is provided.', NULL, '{22e167e8-4284-478f-8531-d44b5a634a86}', 'claude-opus-4-8', 'b2637a5f35001f42', 'active', NULL, '2026-06-16T18:05:50.492955+00:00', '2026-06-16T18:05:50.492988+00:00') ON CONFLICT (intervention_id, condition_id, aspect, arm) DO NOTHING;
