en uncertain (flagged for full text).', 'Emerging', false, 0, 'no sample size or CI in source — precision unknown, flagged for full text', true, 'abstract', 'Per an Open Targets annotation, synthetic conjugated estrogens, B is an approved estrogen receptor agonist (ESR2) indicated for menopause.', 'The drug acts as an estrogen receptor agonist on estrogen receptor 2 (ESR2), restoring estrogenic signaling lost during menopause to relieve symptoms.', '{9d47dbc4-269c-49c5-8717-358e898ebaa7}', 'claude-opus-4-8', 'b2637a5f35001f42', 'active', NULL, '2026-06-16T18:05:56.345093+00:00', '2026-06-16T18:05:56.345129+00:00') ON CONFLICT (intervention_id, condition_id, aspect, arm) DO NOTHING;
