for full text).', 'Emerging', false, 0, 'no sample size or CI in source — precision unknown, flagged for full text', true, 'abstract', 'Triptorelin is annotated as a GnRH receptor agonist and clinical candidate for adenomyosis per Open Targets.', 'As a GnRH receptor agonist, triptorelin suppresses gonadotropin and estrogen production, reducing estrogen-driven adenomyotic tissue activity.', '{363ceaff-5fac-4e57-85ab-35ffc0f5b2dd}', 'claude-opus-4-8', 'b2637a5f35001f42', 'active', NULL, '2026-06-16T18:06:03.536243+00:00', '2026-06-16T18:06:03.536282+00:00') ON CONFLICT (intervention_id, condition_id, aspect, arm) DO NOTHING;
