, true, 'abstract', 'A database annotation lists drospirenone as a clinical candidate for adenomyosis acting as a mineralocorticoid receptor (NR3C2) antagonist, with unknown clinical stage and no supporting study data.', 'Drospirenone may act via mineralocorticoid receptor (NR3C2) antagonism, though its relevance to adenomyosis is not established in the cited claim.', '{f20a1eda-d488-4d4d-a8c4-fea7bb826db6}', 'claude-opus-4-8', 'b2637a5f35001f42', 'active', NULL, '2026-06-16T18:06:12.351044+00:00', '2026-06-16T18:06:12.351128+00:00') ON CONFLICT (intervention_id, condition_id, aspect, arm) DO NOTHING;
