 for full text).', 'Emerging', false, 0, 'no sample size or CI in source — precision unknown, flagged for full text', true, 'abstract', 'Letrozole is a clinical candidate (max stage PHASE_2_3) for adenomyosis acting as a CYP19A1 (aromatase) inhibitor per Open Targets.', 'Letrozole inhibits aromatase (CYP19A1), lowering local estrogen biosynthesis to suppress estrogen-dependent adenomyotic tissue growth.', '{fde30efd-9c60-475f-9365-47af0adeaf2f}', 'claude-opus-4-8', 'b2637a5f35001f42', 'active', NULL, '2026-06-16T18:06:13.792675+00:00', '2026-06-16T18:06:13.792697+00:00') ON CONFLICT (intervention_id, condition_id, aspect, arm) DO NOTHING;
