or CI in source — precision unknown, flagged for full text', true, 'abstract', 'Per a menopause management review, systemic estrogen is first-line therapy and reduces vasomotor symptom frequency by approximately 75%.', 'Estrogen replacement restores hypothalamic thermoregulatory stability disrupted by menopausal estrogen deficiency, reducing hot flashes.', '{0dcb7726-2435-414f-8707-64142d6885d8,d854429f-dba6-4fd7-9b5f-f05a5c713e92}', 'claude-opus-4-8', 'b2637a5f35001f42', 'active', NULL, '2026-06-16T18:08:56.454782+00:00', '2026-06-16T18:08:56.454811+00:00') ON CONFLICT (intervention_id, condition_id, aspect, arm) DO NOTHING;
