own, flagged for full text', true, 'abstract', 'CEE (with or without MPA) is associated with an increased risk of stroke and venous thromboembolism, on the order of about 1 excess event per 1000 person-years.', 'Estrogen-induced procoagulant changes may increase thrombotic and stroke risk.', '{4db320b0-392a-4870-ad11-4aa52816e631,9e0b8488-b143-45bc-9622-4f9a98d45cd8}', 'claude-opus-4-8', 'b2637a5f35001f42', 'active', NULL, '2026-06-16T18:09:09.214875+00:00', '2026-06-16T18:09:09.214902+00:00') ON CONFLICT (intervention_id, condition_id, aspect, arm) DO NOTHING;
