agged for full text', true, 'abstract', 'A review reports that citalopram is associated with an approximately 40% to 65% reduction in the frequency of vasomotor symptoms.', 'As an SSRI, citalopram may modulate central serotonergic pathways involved in thermoregulation, reducing hot flash frequency.', '{76808d06-93f2-41f8-a394-81222e455cdf}', 'claude-opus-4-8', 'b2637a5f35001f42', 'active', NULL, '2026-06-16T18:09:28.218539+00:00', '2026-06-16T18:09:28.218567+00:00') ON CONFLICT (intervention_id, condition_id, aspect, arm) DO NOTHING;
