Female representation not stated — applicability to women uncertain (flagged for full text).', 'Exploratory', false, 0, 'no sample size or CI in source — precision unknown, flagged for full text', true, 'abstract', 'A review states that hormone therapy is not indicated for the prevention of cardiovascular disease.', NULL, '{9734ae33-9af6-49e3-b800-87bbd1d8f0c3}', 'claude-opus-4-8', 'b2637a5f35001f42', 'active', NULL, '2026-06-16T18:09:28.730885+00:00', '2026-06-16T18:09:28.730913+00:00') ON CONFLICT (intervention_id, condition_id, aspect, arm) DO NOTHING;
