l text', true, 'abstract', 'A review reports that venlafaxine is associated with an approximately 40% to 65% reduction in the frequency of menopausal vasomotor symptoms.', 'As an SNRI, venlafaxine may modulate central serotonergic/noradrenergic thermoregulatory pathways to reduce vasomotor symptom frequency.', '{55a7887d-76d4-462d-9f82-f89beb4355f9}', 'claude-opus-4-8', 'b2637a5f35001f42', 'active', NULL, '2026-06-16T18:09:37.476462+00:00', '2026-06-16T18:09:37.476498+00:00') ON CONFLICT (intervention_id, condition_id, aspect, arm) DO NOTHING;
